Very good.
- That was amazing.

103
00:16:36,740 --> 00:16:39,857
I know someone that will be happy

104
00:16:40,020 --> 00:16:43,774
Come on, guys. Dont be afraid

105
00:16:49,660 --> 00:16:51,537
There, no need to hide.

106
00:18:16,300 --> 00:18:21,977
I hear you are going to your grandfather
- Yeah, I intended to go.

107
00:18:22,140 --> 00:18:26,338
Has it been long since you saw him?
- I dont know him.

108
00:18:26,500 --> 00:18:28,775
Perhaps that's why I'm a bit scared

109
00:18:28,940 --> 00:18:33,730
He will be happy to see you.
- I hope so.

110
00:19:02,220 --> 00:19:07,578
Our mixed blood will always be a problem.
Only the yakuza offer us a future.

111
00:19:07,740 --> 00:19:12,291
Why you want to destroy everything
so close to the target?

112
00:19:14,780 --> 00:19:18,216
We've made a mistake, Kien.
From the beginning.

113
00:19:19,260 --> 00:19:24,698
My little sister that knows
and understands everything.

114
00:19:24,860 --> 00:19:29,058
Someday the triads will kill us
for what we have done.

115
00:19:29,220 --> 00:19:32,974
And if they dont do it, Kitano will.

116
00:19:33,140 --> 00:19:36,576
You are wrong.
He needs us.

117
00:19:38,980 --> 00:19:43,974
She didn't make sacrifices
to let us become criminals.

118
00:19:48,340 --> 00:19:53,778
Because of her blood
the triads have banned us.

119
00:19:53,940 --> 00:19:56,454
as outcasts.

120
00:19:59,100 --> 00:20:02,934
Tell me what she has left us...

121
00:20:03,140 --> 00:20:06,530
other than the curse of her blood.

122
00:20:18,140 --> 00:20:22,338
She's dead, Kien.
She didn't abandon us, she's dead.

123
00:20:22,500 --> 00:20:25,094
I will always be there for you.

124
