Hey boys, pass on this message:
Bangkok is a battlefield.

137
00:25:41,540 --> 00:25:43,770
It's not a playground.

138
00:25:47,460 --> 00:25:48,813
Come.

139
00:26:12,140 --> 00:26:16,418
Thanks for your help.
- You are here on his territory.

140
