We just wanted to excersize.

141
00:26:21,700 --> 00:26:23,179
excersize?

142
00:26:24,140 --> 00:26:26,608
He can't see us together.

143
00:26:32,980 --> 00:26:36,416
Go away, or he'll kill you all.

144
00:26:53,580 --> 00:26:57,459
You should have warned us.
- I didn't expect this.

145
00:26:57,620 --> 00:27:03,377
When I came there they wanted to scare me off.
I wasn't raised a coward.

146
00:27:04,740 --> 00:27:09,052
I thought I was done with it.
- Which is not the case.

147
00:27:28,220 --> 00:27:34,295
We have played with our lives.
- Sorry, but I'm not going to give up my gym.

148
00:27:45,620 --> 00:27:49,772
The day when your agression
will dominate you...

149
00:27:49,940 --> 00:27:53,489
it will be too late.

150
00:28:23,260 --> 00:28:26,696
What are you going to do?
- Put my thoughts in order.

151
00:28:26,860 --> 00:28:30,978
If you want to stay, you are welcome.
- thank you.

152
00:28:32,020 --> 00:28:33,738
I've to go too.

153
00:28:33,900 --> 00:28:37,290
And you?
- I'm going home. I've been gone too long.

154
00:28:37,460 --> 00:28:42,215
Let's spend the night here.
Tomorrow we take a morning flight.

155
00:28:50,940 --> 00:28:53,852
Come, we should find a hotel.

156
00:29:08,420 --> 00:29:09,978
Is it far?

157
00:29:37,900 --> 00:29:39,379
Are you counting?

158
00:29:39,540 --> 00:29:44,978
No. They're the names of dead comerades.
I try to keep their memories alive.

159
00:29:46,460 --> 00:29:47,859
What are you talking about?

160
00:29:48,020 --> 00:29:52,332
The war in my village.
I'd rather not talk about it.

161
00:30:20,100 --> 00:30:25,857
It's me. Is he there?
- Yes he is. Do you want to speak to him?

162
00:30:26,020 --> 00:30:28,375
You want to talk with him.
- Put him on the phone

163
00:30:28,540 --> 00:30:29,893
take it easy.

164
00:30:30,060 --> 00:30:34,576
I'm far away, but I love you
and think about you a lot.

165
00:30:34,780 --> 00:30:38,614
Really?
- You shouldn't doubt that.

166
00:30:38,820 --> 00:30:42,335
Do you still have my necklace?
- I will never take it off.

167
00:30:42,540 --> 00:30:47,660
Daddy, I miss you
- I love you and your mother a lot.

168
00:30:47,860 --> 00:30:50,613
Mommy, daddy has to tell you something.

169
00:30:51,860 --> 00:30:53,339
Hello, yes?

170
00:30:53,540 --> 00:30:56,100
Everything ok with you?
- I'm good.

171
00:30:57,540 --> 00:31:01,613
Tell me...
What do you want me to say?

172
00:31:01,820 --> 00:31:05,608
Bye.
- Bye. Take care of yourself.

173
00:31:05,820 --> 00:31:10,132
See you soon.
- Right, yeah. See you soon

174
00:31:28,660 --> 00:31:32,130
Divorced?
- No, just far from eachother.

175
00:31:33,700 --> 00:31:36,453
And you?
- I didn't find the right one yet.

176
00:31:36,620 --> 00:31:38,815
Different than others.

177
00:32:00,100 --> 00:32:01,453
Kien?

178
00:32:22,620 --> 00:32:24,338
Come on in.

179
00:32:32,540 --> 00:32:35,100
You got a plan?

180
00:32:35,260 --> 00:32:40,015
I dont travel thousands of kilometers
just to fight in Bangkok.

181
00:32:40,220 --> 00:32:43,530
That's not for me anymore.

182
00:32:43,700 --> 00:32:47,613
I should have asked her.
- who? the small asian?

183
00:32:47,780 --> 00:32:52,410
She's on the wrong side.
- I dont want to judge her so soon.

184
00:32:52,580 --> 00:32:57,813
Have you already forgotten what happened?
- I know

185
00:32:57,980 --> 00:33:02,815
She only brings troubles. Forget about her.

186
00:33:10,260 --> 00:33:13,332
Kenjee, dont ruin your life.
He's not worth it.

187
00:33:14,780 --> 00:33:19,900
No!
Cut it out, Kenjee. No!

188
00:34:24,420 --> 00:34:26,809
What are you doing here?

189
00:34:26,980 --> 00:34:29,414
Relax, it's cool.

190
00:34:36,860 --> 00:34:40,455
Leave me alone.
- Can't we talk?

191
00:34:58,020 --> 00:35:01,695
What are you afraid of?
You came looking for me.

192
00:35:10,380 --> 00:35:14,293
Go away. Please.

193
00:35:33,660 --> 00:35:36,538
Daddy.
- My boy.

194
00:35:37,940 --> 00:35:42,616
I'm glad to receive you
here with me in my house.

195
00:35:42,780 --> 00:35:46,136
I'm only here to make
my daughter happy.

196
00:35:46,300 --> 00:35:52,057
It is good to reconcile our families
and cultures with each other.

197
00:35:52,220 --> 00:35:58,614
Our ways are too different.
You will never understand that.

198
00:36:00,380 --> 00:36:05,500
An old rule of our triad says
I will never be able to trust you.

199
00:36:10,180 --> 00:36:13,490
Kitano.
- I'm sorry. I've to go.

200
00:36:27,540 --> 00:36:30,452
Thank you for this second chance.

201
00:36:35,060 --> 00:36:39,019
Wong has been waiting a while for
someone to follow him up.

202
00:36:39,180 --> 00:36:43,856
This kidnapping will break his heart.
- I will not disappoint you again.

203
00:37:00,780 --> 00:37:03,772
I'll be right back.
- Are you crazy?

204
00:39:06,660 --> 00:39:09,857
Not today, guys.
Come back tomorrow.

205
00:39:17,420 --> 00:39:20,890
They got away good.
- Do you want to trump them?

206
00:39:21,060 --> 00:39:23,654
It is tempting.
- What?

207
00:39:24,700 --> 00:39:27,089
I wont be part of it.

208
00:39:27,260 --> 00:39:28,898
Yaguy, Come for a second

209
00:39:34,020 --> 00:39:36,488
He is right, he's a father.

210
00:39:36,660 --> 00:39:41,575
But I'm in.
Otherwise I can forget about my gym

211
00:39:41,740 --> 00:39:45,619
We take him to the airport
and tackle them.

212
00:39:45,780 --> 00:39:47,930
Alright, but quickly.

213
00:40:30,860 --> 00:40:35,172
Take me with you...

214
00:40:46,020 --> 00:40:48,659
There she is.
There.

215
00:40:54,820 --> 00:40:56,890
Tsu, Kien wants to talk to you.

216
00:40:57,060 --> 00:41:00,450
Tell him he solves it by himself
- Do it yourself.

217
00:41:00,620 --> 00:41:03,453
That idiot still doesn't understand.

218
00:41:04,900 --> 00:41:07,050
Mind your own business.

219
00:41:26,860 --> 00:41:28,213
Hurry.

220
00:41:39,420 --> 00:41:41,012
This way.

221
00:41:49,980 --> 00:41:51,333
Come with me

222
00:41:54,820 --> 00:41:56,173
Trust me.

223
00:43:38,380 --> 00:43:41,577
Your grandfather knew that you would come

224
00:43:41,740 --> 00:43:47,292
He has told me so much about you
that I know you better than yourself.

225
00:44:08,660 --> 00:44:13,688
You have come a long way.
- Thank you for seeing me.

226
00:44:13,860 --> 00:44:20,129
Your grandfather would have been proud if
he knew you would be amongst his people.

227
00:44:20,300 --> 00:44:23,736
I should have come much sooner.

228
00:44:23,900 --> 00:44:29,452
He's still here, you know.
His spirit still waits for you.

229
00:44:29,620 --> 00:44:33,295
This temple is his residence
He has not left it.

230
00:44:33,460 --> 00:44:36,452
He's here and there. Everywhere at once

231
00:44:36,620 --> 00:44:42,092
He's in the trees.
He's in the wind. He's in you

232
00:46:03,340 --> 00:46:06,218
They will never find us here.
- I want an explanation

233
00:46:06,380 --> 00:46:11,613
What do you want with my life story?
- Maybe I want to stay then

234
00:46:12,780 --> 00:46:16,216
You wont understand anyway
- We shall see.

235
00:46:17,380 --> 00:46:23,091
He took care for me when I was small.
Without him I would be dead.

236
00:46:23,420 --> 00:46:26,537
I can't just abandon him.

237
00:46:27,860 --> 00:46:29,851
What is he to you?

238
00:46:31,500 --> 00:46:32,853
My brother.

239
00:46:43,820 --> 00:46:45,856
Let me help you then.

240
00:46:55,980 --> 00:46:59,256
<i>Wong has been waiting long for
someone to follow him up.</i>

241
00:46:59,420 --> 00:47:02,537
<i>This kidnapping will break his heart.</i>

242
00:47:19,060 --> 00:47:21,210
Kitano was very serious.

243
00:47:22,260 --> 00:47:25,457
We can also do it without her.

244
00:47:25,620 --> 00:47:30,455
But what did she do with him?
Can't she see that he is dangerous?

245
00:47:30,620 --> 00:47:34,215
You always think too much
It is time for action.

246
00:47:34,380 --> 00:47:37,019
Thinking ahead prevent mistakes.

247
00:47:37,180 --> 00:47:41,890
Tell that to your sister.
It's her fault that it came this far.

248
00:47:42,060 --> 00:47:46,531
After the kidnapping Kitano
will take us into his group.

